\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u(x,y)=\sum_{n_{x}=1}^{\infty}c_{n_{x}}(y)\sin\left(\frac{n_{x}\pi x}{L_{x}}\right),
\]

\end_inset

with different coefficients 
\begin_inset Formula $c_{n_{x}}$
